{"about_the_game":"<i>The demo is a full, older version of the game. The current version has much more content, options and UI features. Anything you unlock in the demo will carry over</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/desc1.png?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Before you lies the <strong>Path of Achra</strong>...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/naquia.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Inspired by the dungeons of Tales of Maj Eyal, Dungeon Crawl Stone Soup and Rift Wizard, it is the ongoing passion project of a solo developer, who humbly thanks you for visiting<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/desc2.png?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Merge culture, class and religion to establish a starting hero, unlock more options as you play, with 1000+ potential combinations<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/choica.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Customize your hero with 50+ elementally-aligned powers such as Pyrokinesis, Necromancy, Blood Retort, Obedient Ice...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/powersa.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Discover and freely equip unique weapons and armor with impactful abilities<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/weaponsa.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Explosive synergies await...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/impa.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/desc3.png?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>A &quot;broken build sandbox&quot; - create devastating combos by combining triggered effects. Shoot bolts of lightning when you pierce enemies with vines, teleport while emitting psychic beams, etc...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/steamQamar.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>If you wish, summon armies of powerful allies<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/necroa.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Swiftly play through levels with automove commands. With caution! Enemies can be brutal...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/impdeath.gif?t=1735920523\" /><br><br><br>Seek the mysterious Obelisk, as the world floods behind you...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128270/extras/warriora.gif?t=1735920523\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Green Tower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2128270/df284e0bdf759c723f553456b6f2834a9bd3a21f.jpg"},{"name":"The Violet Tower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2128270/7a8506cba3493058ca6f10393d5016c1a0b0ff4d.jpg"},{"name":"The Red Tower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2128270/dd0b98267a2c2af82ad7efb71ccede32aaa92105.jpg"},{"name":"The Obelisk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2128270/3d57030fe6035a84604a2f4607ba89d96699e2ac.jpg"},{"name":"Walk the Path","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2128270/6015ff5a8b34748086308a26620f1a7aa986db30.jpg"},{"name":"The God at the End of the World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm